channel.title: [SRL] Willow power fletcher
channel.description:
[center]Ub3r |<1||3r's Willow powerfletcher [V 8.0][/center]
What This does: Chops willows until the inventory is full, then it uses the knife on the log and starts making them into whatever the user chose, ( long / short ). Repeats this process.
When it was made: Before villavu.com has been gone.
Is it being updated?: No updates at the moment. Post bugs / fixes if any.
Disclaimer: I am not responsible for any of my scripts doing any harm to your characters offence status. This includes rule number 7 in runescape ( of course ). If you are banned or runescape has detected the use of this macro, Please post about this.
Extra Notes: This script only supports one player at the moment.
RULES: Please do not abuse this macro, play legit every 2 hours if possible.
WARNING!: DO NOT RUN FOR MORE THAN 4 HOURS OR YOU ARE BANNED FOR SURE.
